$lang['faq_preg1']="What is Foodinea?";
$lang['faq_res1']="Foodinea is the Latin America leader platform to book tours and activities for Foodies platform. With us, you can book tours and activities in advance:  this way you get the best prices and you can plan your gastronomic adventure with the advantage of not needing to deal with cash once you're in your destination. Your mission: Enjoy your adventure through your palate.";
$lang['faq_preg2']="What types of tours and activities are offered on Foodinea?";
$lang['faq_res2']="We offer tours and activities for foodies, wine lovers and culinary adventurers.Enjoy authentic Mexican tacos, eat barbecue as Argentinian, or enjoy a gourmet dinner at the Chef´s House. In Foodinea We have over 400 authentic dining experiences in Mexico, Chile and Argentina to make your trip a memorable one. Expect our next destinations; so book a tour, and discover Latin America eating like a local.";
